high_descs: Turn left and walk to the other side of a countertop next to you.
Pick up a lettuce from the countertop.
Turn left, walk straight parallel to the countertop, continue to the other part of the room divided by a wall on the right, turn right when passing that wall and head to a sidetable with a microwave.
Put the lettuce on the sidetable.
Go to a diningtable that stands against the opposite wall.
Pick up a knife from the diningtable.
Go back to the sidetable.
Using the knife, cut the lettuce on the sidetable.
